{"tid":2245227,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人為什麼不能殺人？","createTime":"2020-10-16T05:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T14:56:31.000Z","uid":128220,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"81b24a5c3a62b0a0665c8896f59f3ff026230702","tid":2245227,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rgZoJi2CwR0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrgZoJi2CwR0&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=6df7806a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rgZoJi2CwR0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">酒鬼薔薇聖斗事件（神戸連続児童殺傷事件），是1997年發生在日本兵庫縣神戶市須磨區的一宗連續殺人案。案件中造成2人死亡、3人重傷，被殺害者皆為國小生。14歲犯人東慎一郎於同年6月28日被逮捕，由於行為血腥殘忍，進行包括分屍、破壞屍體、寄送挑戰書等犯行，因而衝擊整個日本社會。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n犯案後公開向警察宣戰<br />\n<em><span class=\"large\">酒鬼薔薇聖斗的遊戲要開始了。愚鈍的警察諸君，試著來阻止我吧。關於殺人我感到非常的愉快。好想看到人的死亡。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n唔係要討論，點解人要殺人<br />\n係想講，點解有人可以無緣無故殺人<br />\n仲要係殺死小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953426ca42f49eee7286208f7bb747dde1b9d976","tid":2245227,"uid":305638,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"大人佢殺唔到"},{"pid":"08e9b5bb9ee424e7e3acc7e3c67af6360afc9a1d","tid":2245227,"uid":266382,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"如果佢殺嘅係黑社會大佬咁又點睇"},{"pid":"97a1e62caa2a27c280e95524ac15d3ba4ae1a291","tid":2245227,"uid":258899,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"比自以為文明嘅人類覺得自己好文明"},{"pid":"d4024351cf3198b4588ae6b0b8fc43f6d2008c1f","tid":2245227,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T05:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9TAnPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9TAnPc.jpg&h=3a857b9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38a8311f1deffbe30c2fdc38f6e42fd8036056a7","tid":2245227,"uid":76978,"